North Central buy back plan approved . North Central Bancshares Inc said on Wednesday that it received regulatory approval from the Office of Thrift Supervision today for a stock repurchase program . The program authorizes the company to repurchase up to 10 percent of its 3 . 8 million outstanding shares of common stock . The repurchases will be made from time to time , during a six month period in open market and privately negotiated transactions , at the discretion of management , the company said . Shares of North Central closed down 3 / 8 at 12 - 5 / 8 Wednesday . - - Reuters Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 
